{"primaryContentSections":[{"declarations":[{"platforms":["iOS"],"languages":["occ"],"tokens":[{"kind":"text","text":"+ ("},{"preciseIdentifier":"c:v","text":"void","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":") ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"clearNotificationCenter"},{"kind":"text","text":";"}]}],"kind":"declarations"},{"kind":"content","content":[{"type":"heading","anchor":"discussion","text":"Discussion","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Removes all notifications delivered by your app from the iOS Notification Center.","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"text":"This is commonly used when:","type":"text"}]},{"items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"User opens the app (clear notifications since they’re viewing content)"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"User logs out (clear notifications for privacy)","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Content is marked as read in-app","type":"text"}]}]},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"Performing a “mark all as read” action"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"type":"unorderedList"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Only removes notifications from your app; other apps’ notifications are unaffected.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"text":"Example","type":"heading","anchor":"Example","level":2},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"Clear notifications on app activation and logout:","type":"text"}]},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["class NotificationManager {","","    func applicationDidBecomeActive() {","        \/\/ Clear notifications when user opens app","        Pushwoosh.configure.clearNotificationCenter()","","        \/\/ Also reset badge","        UIApplication.shared.applicationIconBadgeNumber = 0","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(0)","    }","","    func handleUserLogout() {","        \/\/ Clear notifications for privacy","        Pushwoosh.configure.clearNotificationCenter()","","        \/\/ Unregister from push","        Pushwoosh.configure.unregisterForPushNotifications { _ in }","","        \/\/ Clear user identity","        Pushwoosh.configure.setUserId(\"\")","    }","","    func markAllAsRead() {","        \/\/ Clear from notification center","        Pushwoosh.configure.clearNotificationCenter()","","        \/\/ Update backend","        APIClient.shared.markAllNotificationsRead { _ in }","","        \/\/ Clear badge","        Pushwoosh.configure.sendBadges(0)","    }","}"]}]}],"kind":"symbol","hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration"]]},"abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Clears all delivered notifications from the notification center."}],"sections":[],"metadata":{"roleHeading":"Type Method","title":"clearNotificationCenter","symbolKind":"method","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"clearNotificationCenter"}],"modules":[{"name":"PushwooshCore"}],"role":"symbol","fragments":[{"text":"+ ","kind":"text"},{"kind":"identifier","text":"clearNotificationCenter"}],"externalID":"c:objc(pl)PWConfiguration(cm)clearNotificationCenter"},"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"occ","url":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore\/PWConfiguration\/clearNotificationCenter"},"schemaVersion":{"minor":3,"patch":0,"major":0},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"occ"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/pushwooshcore\/pwconfiguration\/clearnotificationcenter"]}],"references":{"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/documentation/PushwooshCore":{"url":"\/documentation\/pushwooshcore","abstract":[{"type":"text","text":"Core foundation module for Pushwoosh SDK."}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore\/documentation\/PushwooshCore","title":"PushwooshCore","role":"collection","type":"topic"},"doc://com.pushwoosh.PushwooshCore/document